data.description: Almost New! Built in 2019. Introducing a Stunning Flynn Built Home that offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and style. Upon entering you are greeted by an inviting interior! Nice open floorpan. Light and Bright! The heart of this home is the impressive open kitchen, complete with a stylish center island, quartz countertops and an array of desirable upgrades. Spacious Master bedroom with walk in closets. Only carpeting is in the bedrooms. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home is located on a sprawling 2.48 acre lot. The property offers the perfect balance of cleared and wooded area, providing natural beauty and privacy. Garden area, floating deck with turf perfect for grilling. Shed included. The fenced yard adds privacy and seclusion and is perfect for relaxation and recreation. Call today!
